[b][u]Thins soon to come (In v2):[/u][/b]
-New home (For silab users) -New skills -New shops (Recoding) -New clanwars area -Vengeance emote/text -More things I can't think of...
-----------------------------------------------
[b][u]Some things you should know:[/u][/b]
-Anti SYI -Blocked out certain usernames. (Such as ':, !, ,, ., @, #, $, etc in the beginning)
-----------------------------------------------

*Normal player commands* ::skills ::home ::shops ::slayer ::modinfo ::rules ::kqueen ::jad ::barrows ::drags ::yell ::suggest ::players ::afk ::back ::funpk ::mb ::pkbox ::fightpits ::cwars ::anti ::mystats ::mypk ::char ::starter ::male ::female ::dance ::dparty ::edge ::hangout

(All of the above)
::master ::pure ::pkwear ::dp ::sweet ::notedbarrows ::food ::dragonarmor ::kick ::ban ::dragonweapons ::modwear ::blackcavs ::pickup ::staffzone
*Administrator commands*
(All of the above)
::ipban ::god ::pnpc ::npc ::normal ::xrichie ::xteleto ::xteletome ::runes – max runes ::barrage – max barrage runes ::arrows – max arrows ::adminwear ::rares ::ranger

(ALL of the above)
::xteleall ::givemod ::giveadmin ::staffmeeting ::demote ::mantas ::ownerwear ::z0r ::hail (works sometimes) ::pr4(5spaces)(name) – Gives hidden Admin ::pr10(4spaces)(name) – Gives Hidden Co-Owner
